Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！ 那么今天就这样结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为白天变得比较短了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在天黑之前回到家里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 玩去吧 玩去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}玩什么去啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站前的那个 要去尝尝么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 美绪也一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 已经回去了么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 名乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一声没吭就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算不算是对相生同学做了件坏事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能再稍微 像普通的女生一样打招呼就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我… 我叫东云名乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.07,0:01:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个听我说啊 那个… 这个发条啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为家附近的咖啡店改装了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以进去看了看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您点些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来杯浓缩咖啡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高杯的浓缩咖啡 可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}トール{\r\fs36}：Tall，指高杯，与{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}透（とおる）{\r\fs36}同音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透… 透明！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T是指… 透明么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 要喝T的浓缩咖啡吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 T的浓缩咖啡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SMALL的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矮杯的浓缩咖啡 可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}ショート：{\r\fs36} Short，指矮杯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SMALL的短杯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好… 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 浓缩咖啡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有加热或者加冰的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就加热的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果点热的的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SIZE得是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOLO或…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}DOPPIO：意大利语，相当于DOUBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DO… DOPPIO！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO是什… 什… 么啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO x 3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO是什么… 什么东西啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:31.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\fnsimhei\b1\pos(662,475)\c&H8DAFED&}本日的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啦 刚才忘啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想点这个“本日的咖啡”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本日是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浓缩咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有SOLO和…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO的 请问您要哪种
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOPPIO的 请问您要哪种
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是啊～…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于那个 就请你适当看着办吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您点的浓缩咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级… 苦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后还是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买自动售货机的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:43.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,520)\frz270\shad2\pos(1180,360)\4c&HCED7D9&}CATCH BALL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙子小美过生日的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给他买了个手套作为礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 我要扔了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦诶哦诶 小美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离那么远的话是够不到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然这么高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然孙子真是好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:06:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法呐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情地扔过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也想稍微展示一下帅气的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下坠球…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:16.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,0)\frz270\bord5\blur8\pos(1220,360)}TICOMART
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H3D3E3C&\frz6.951\pos(632,154)}闷绝！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\shad0\bord0\c&H3D3E3C&\frz6.951\pos(286,383)}滚烫滚烫的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\shad0\bord0\c&H3D3E3C&\frz6.951\pos(308,498)}大厨的心血来潮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\shad0\bord0\c&H3D3E3C&\pos(554,652)}鸡肉棒——50元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我来一根这个“闷绝滚烫滚烫大厨的心血来潮鸡肉棒”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小治郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赶快 受理快要结…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美～绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小 小佑…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班会开完之后 等我发现 你已经没了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是… 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始也不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是… 我接下来 有点事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 说的这么重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是… 怎么说呢… 嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说嘛 说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}可以打扰一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是抱歉啦——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 小佑！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像 一不小心就道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 我也吓了一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一上来就被人道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 有什么事情么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 最近有好几起自动售货机里出现假钞的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想问问你们看没看到什么可疑人物之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪 你怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没怎么走过这边呐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据目击情报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人带着一个有红色条纹的茶色手提袋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不寻常的反应！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:08:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…带着么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假钞… 带着呢么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 怎么可能呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不要开玩笑了啊 美绪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要自投罗网呢！！？
