Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把假钞拿出来啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到… 竟然真的带着啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样… 就请饶了我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样请您 饶了我吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一张吗！？ 假钞？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才不是假钞！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是货真价实的贿赂！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不明白你说什么呢！！
