Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佑 借我橡皮好么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪边？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 借我橡皮呗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人形橡皮！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这哪能擦掉啊 只会越擦越脏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佑 借我橡皮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣也没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法呐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 哪边？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边×2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:14:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行×N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则是你们一个一个来 刚才不算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这规则什么时候才是头啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 从麻衣开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请 请
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您自由调查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫… 好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damage攻击可是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 One Pena哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One Pena是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}One Penalty：犯规一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One Penalty哦
