Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总不能出握着东西的那边吧
