Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 打扰了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？ 没人在家么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 马上过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 久等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎怎怎怎… 怎么办啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么相生同学来家里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是见到了博士的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}来了～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器人的身份肯定会暴露的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}啊 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}啊咧？ 名乃呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}名乃倒是就在那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}难道是名乃的同学么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定只是来给我送卷子或者什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}哦哦 快进来快进来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 就在玄关这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}请进 请进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}请不用费心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已经进来了那就没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好在博士乱说话之前就替相生同学把事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 肚子好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 刚才的声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只叫阪本的猫 他能说话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能的嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪… 阪本先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你快点说喵！ 说喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 为什么我到现在了还要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说喵 阪本先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵 喵…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？ 就是只猫而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有客人来了 你先去外面玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有好好打个招呼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是相生佑子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 你是名乃的妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我是博士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我制造了名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是个孩子但是好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为博士是博士嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不… 不是哦 相生同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亲戚的孩子 父母都在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为到晚上都不能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮着照顾她到他们回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吧？ 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！！ 笨蛋——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我重新给你上点茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 名乃 稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶的话 就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:18:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请喝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉～～害！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边是枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级帅——！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 完蛋啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 接下来是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耍帅句子大对决！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 从不才佑子我来开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 开玩笑的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你快起来啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～！ 好帅！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是博士！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独角仙～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生同学到底是来干嘛的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放上去了 放上去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认输了！认输了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小！好小！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.23,0:19:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有事啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天多谢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叨扰多时 抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那个 相生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊… 实际上…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在学习变戏法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是什么机器人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃不是机器人这回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃就是名乃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不就可以了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就是来跟你说这个的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都差点忘记了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 回见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是 你再方便的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！！ 会来会来！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次画画吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要画鲨鱼的画！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}鲨鱼吗？ 好帅气啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很帅的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲨鱼 我喜欢～！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}鲨鱼～ 博士 你喜欢鲨鱼的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲨鱼 喜欢 因为鲨鱼很帅嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}鲨鱼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲨鱼鲨鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次～！ 再来一次～！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来再来…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲨鱼鲨鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士～ 我也要来！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲨鱼～！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:22:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 阪本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.42,0:23:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.51,0:23:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.90,0:23:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.72,0:23:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花螺丝钉 这个名字真好听
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.72,0:23:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}译注：日文是{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}プラスネジ{\r\fs36}，前面的{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}プラス{\r\fs36}等于Plus
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.12,0:23:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种积极向上的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.45,0:23:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生就是要 不管如何都要向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.54,0:23:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话的日常是第十七话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.13,0:21:46.72,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}みんなで歌おう　心を一つにして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:57.27,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}悲しい時も　つらい時も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.98,0:22:08.49,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}みんなで歌おう　大きな声を出して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:19.00,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}はずかしがらず　歌おうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.05,0:22:29.64,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}心燃える歌が　歌が　きっと君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:40.48,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}きらめけ世界中に　僕の歌をのせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:53.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1000)\blur3}きらめけ世界中に　届け愛のメッセージ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.13,0:21:46.72,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}大家来歌唱吧 将心凝聚到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:57.27,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}在那悲伤的时候 在那艰难的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.98,0:22:08.49,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}大家来歌唱吧 放出洪亮的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:19.00,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不要害羞 来歌唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.05,0:22:29.64,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}唱一曲振奋心灵的歌 这一曲必将传至你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:40.48,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}在这闪耀的世界中 装载上我的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:53.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1000)\blur3}在这闪耀的世界中 传递爱的讯息

Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:15.57,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD040BE&\4c&HD040BE&}上々　友情！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:16.74,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD040BE&\4c&HD040BE&}万事　まじ　快調！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:19.33,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD040BE&\4c&HD040BE&}ななななななな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.70,0:01:25.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD040BE&\4c&HD040BE&}はい　言っちゃいましょ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.08,0:01:26.75,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD040BE&\4c&HD040BE&}キミは　Best Best Friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.84,0:01:29.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(640,660)}{\c&HC48DEC&\4c&HC48DEC&}Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.13,0:01:31.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちょっと　ふざけてみたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:31.50,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(640,660)}{\c&HC48DEC&\4c&HC48DEC&}Shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:33.63,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっと　ふざけ返してくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:35.38,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(640,660)}{\c&HC48DEC&\4c&HC48DEC&}Lan Lan Lan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:36.01,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居心地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.05,0:01:37.55,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いいったら　ありゃしない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:38.76,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(640,660)}{\c&HC48DEC&\4c&HC48DEC&}Why
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:40.81,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,イヤなことあったって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:41.10,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(640,660)}{\c&HC48DEC&\4c&HC48DEC&}Fine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:43.98,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}そっこー　忘れちゃうんだ
